Title: Aerobics Meltdown
Writer: Keegan-Michael Key (creator), Jordan Peele (creator), Rebecca Drysdale, Colton Dunn, Phil Augusta Jackson, Jay Martel, Ian Roberts, Alex Rubens, Charlie Sanders, Rich Talarico
Actors: Keegan-Michael Key, Jordan Peele, Lindsay Ames, Hayden Faraday
Plot: Stan Lee pitches some new superheroes, a guy loses his street cred when he experiences a brain freeze, and a man develops a complex mnemonic device to remember where he parked.
